Document: NinePatchRect
Path: godot/classes/class_ninePatchRect.rst
Summary: Describes the NinePatchRect node, which scales textures cleanly using a 3x3 grid.

NinePatchRect produces clean panels of any size based on a small texture. To do so, it splits the texture in a 3x3 grid. When you scale the node, it tiles the texture's edges horizontally or vertically, tiles the center on both axes, and leaves the corners unchanged.
